title: Faahfaahinta hantida
safetyInfoDescription: Sifooyinka badbaadada caadiga ah oo ku jira
weaponsOnProperty: Ma jiraan hub hantida ku yaal?
securityCameras: Ma jiraan kamaradaha ammaanka hantida ku yaal?
minLengthWarning: Ugu yaraan {{min}} xaraf ayaa loo baahan yahay
tipContent: Baadh hantiyo kula mid ah aagagaaga si aad qiime tartan u dejiso. Had iyo jeer waxaad wax ka beddeli kartaa qiimayaashaaga dabadeed iyadoo ku saleysan baahida.
